DarkMouse:: 

She transformed into mouse mode and started to walk off the bridge.  
She turned and looked at Galvatron. "Why would that other base be a 
problem? If your cloaked, and they can't even deteck this base, then 
why would they be a threat. Unless they have a way to locate this 
place, we should be fine. Shouldn't we?" Her nose for trouble 
twitched. But her body was tired and all she wanted was sleep at the 
moment.
